// An entry self-loop with an orphan self-loop node that's unreachable from the entry. The
// structurer only walks nodes reachable from `entry`, so node 1 is invisible to it and the
// output is just the entry's loop. The `// unstructured blocks` notice doesn't fire for
// unreachable nodes - dead bytecode in the input is excluded from the detection set (see
// the `reachable` filter in `mod.rs::structure`).
//
//   ->0     ->1
//    \_|     \_|

code,0,0
code,1,1
